[{"index":1,"title":"【葛琪琪】人物分析贴","content":"嘻哈里的所有女角色我都喜欢。葛琪琪是我最爱的一个女角色。葛琪琪作为四小只里唯一一个没有任何背景的普通女生，最让我感同身受。不过也让我对刘飒颇多怨念，尤其是对比两男主的复杂的背景设定后。<br><br><br>作者若深爱自己的角色，一定会认真处理角色的背景与人际关系。<br>比如男主毛，科技二代，父母莫名失踪。所以毛一直在努力学习变得强大，就是为了有一天能找回自己的父母。<br>再比如男二上官帅，上官集团二代继承人，高富帅学霸一枚。温柔的的的母亲早逝，极度渴望母爱，思念母亲。而变态的父亲对帅从小实行打压式“鸡娃”教育，导致帅极端追求完美，希望以此得到父亲的一点点关心与肯定。<br>GiGi，无父无母的机器人，一切言行举止都是程序计算出来的。不懂人情世故。<br><br>再说琪琪，父母健在，根据剧情可推出其父母是开明的小资家庭。对比其他帅毛gi，可以说是家庭生活最幸福的一个了。<br>问题是琪琪的父母连出场都没有，只以画外音出场了一次。<br>为什么我会不满呢？一个丰富立体的角色，她一定是多维度的。她的经历亲情友情爱情师生情等等，以及角色自身成长所面临的各种困惑、心理挣扎和自我矛盾，这才是一个好角色的魅力所在。<br><br>而我亲爱的琪琪，亲情部分约等于无。哪怕是刘飒多画一页琪琪与家人相处的画面也好啊，让读者看到琪琪在家庭中的境遇。亦让琪琪的人物形象与层次更加丰富。<br><br>好在琪琪的爱情与友情线和自我成长线够精彩。让读者看到了一个鲜活可爱的葛琪琪。也让我爱上了琪琪，对琪琪念念不忘。","author":"Xjgxjm1984000","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.f276693b.XEeKSIB8_8UeeDT5GmzAxA?t=1625918276&fr=pb","date":"2021-09-20 12:31","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":2,"title":"回复：【葛琪琪】人物分析贴","content":"先让我拉踩一下嘻哈主角团的名字：葛琪琪、Gi Gi、毛小蒙、上官帅。<br>🆘，名字是人的一张名片。<br>一个好的名字反映出很多事情：父母的经济文化程度，和对孩子的期望与爱，甚至家庭气氛（比如孩子随母姓，母亲地位很可能比较高，家庭氛围更倾向于男女平等<br>等等。）<br><br>狗飒你给主角团起名字为何如此敷衍随意！！<br>葛琪琪，一听就是个大众普通的邻家女孩名字，毫无新意<img class=\"BDE_Smiley\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\" changedsize=\"false\" src=\"https://gsp0.baidu.com/5aAHeD3nKhI2p27j8IqW0jdnxx1xbK/tb/editor/images/client/image_emoticon10.png\" >。狗飒，你对自己的女主角名字能不能用点心！<br><br>Gi Gi，不是我思想不纯洁，往歪了想，是这个名字发音真的很容易让人想歪尴尬啊。更靠谱的叫法是“叽叽喳喳”的“叽叽”。Gi Gi的确是个能跟🦜吵架的活泼小话痨。但狗飒取名一定要怎么直白吗？<br>（毛小蒙，拜托你好好学习语文吧！）<br><br>上官帅，真的帅，全身上下无一不透露着帅气。但你名字直接叫帅？😂😂<br>我甚至幻想过，如果嘻哈改编成动画，叫上官彻怎么样？彻彻底底的彻。可是不行，嘻哈剧情已经与各自的名字绑定，再改就变味了。唉……<br><br>（现实告诉我们，帅哥还是帅而不自知比较帅，比如杨洋）<br><br>毛小蒙，人确实毛毛躁躁，还有点迷糊。<br>但狗飒，你的主角名字除了能反映主角性格外，烂大街了！<br>对比隔壁《撞上》，真是被碾压。","author":"Xjgxjm1984000","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.f276693b.XEeKSIB8_8UeeDT5GmzAxA?t=1625918276&fr=pb","date":"2021-09-20 14:00","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":3,"title":"回复：【葛琪琪】人物分析贴","content":"言归正传，琪琪是一个追求完美的女孩，亦希望在别人眼里自己是个“完美女孩”。<br><br>可是琪琪，没有人是完美的。人外有人 天外有天。看看琪琪自己对“完美女孩”是怎么定义的：<img class=\"BDE_Image\" src=\"http://tiebapic.baidu.com/forum/w%3D580/sign=669cf66c25f0f736d8fe4c093a54b382/418ca986c9177f3eaaf13c1e2dcf3bc79e3d56a5.jpg?tbpicau=2023-05-01-05_c342834c9c73c4114fa6faec4d603fb9\" size=\"555004\" changedsize=\"true\" width=\"560\" height=\"995\" size=\"555004\">","author":"Xjgxjm1984000","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.f276693b.XEeKSIB8_8UeeDT5GmzAxA?t=1625918276&fr=pb","date":"2021-09-20 15:49","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":4,"title":"回复：【葛琪琪】人物分析贴","content":"琪琪对“完美”的总结就是：外表整洁干净，学习成绩优异，礼貌待人。<br>（那个对着镜子练习过N次微笑的琪琪真厉害啊，idol自律了。像我这种想笑就笑管别人怎么看的人望尘莫及）","author":"Xjgxjm1984000","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.f276693b.XEeKSIB8_8UeeDT5GmzAxA?t=1625918276&fr=pb","date":"2021-09-20 15:56","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":5,"title":"回复：【葛琪琪】人物分析贴","content":"我好爱这个神采奕奕，热爱生活，认真对待每一天的琪琪。","author":"Xjgxjm1984000","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.f276693b.XEeKSIB8_8UeeDT5GmzAxA?t=1625918276&fr=pb","date":"2021-09-20 15:58","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":6,"title":"回复：【葛琪琪】人物分析贴","content":"琪琪应该是那种别人家的孩子，品貌、学习、道德俱佳的三好学生。从小生活在充满爱与期望的环境里，一路顺风顺水地长大。<br>直到那个阳光明媚的日子，遇到上官帅。","author":"Xjgxjm1984000","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.f276693b.XEeKSIB8_8UeeDT5GmzAxA?t=1625918276&fr=pb","date":"2021-09-20 16:06","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":7,"title":"回复：【葛琪琪】人物分析贴","content":"波伏娃说过，女人是被塑造的。<br>从古至今，无数的神话传说与铺天盖地的言情小说电影电视剧给女性造了一个英雄救美的爱情梦。在这场英雄救美中，女性总是被动地等待着男性的救助，而不是自己拿起剑与恶魔战斗自救。<br>似乎，被一个男人拯救就是一个女人一生最大的幸福。而女人为此要付出自己的一生。<br>而无数血淋淋的事实告诉女人这英雄救美的爱情梦不过是父权体制下诱导女性向下的的谎言。可等女性幡然悔悟想要回头时却为时已晚。她的青春年华早已耗尽了。<br>正处于青春期三观未定型的葛琪琪，亦有一个英雄救美的爱情梦。","author":"Xjgxjm1984000","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.f276693b.XEeKSIB8_8UeeDT5GmzAxA?t=1625918276&fr=pb","date":"2021-09-20 16:27","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":8,"title":"回复：【葛琪琪】人物分析贴","content":"看看琪琪对优秀男生的定义：三好学生，高学历+优良品德，勇敢又有正义感，像她一样完美。<br><img class=\"BDE_Image\" src=\"http://tiebapic.baidu.com/forum/w%3D580/sign=39aff5c8262762d0803ea4b790ed0849/e3b48c025aafa40fdbb88436ee64034f79f019a7.jpg?tbpicau=2023-05-01-05_762dfc4894d650a3986a84f8b098b566\" size=\"549231\" changedsize=\"true\" width=\"560\" height=\"995\" size=\"549231\"><img class=\"BDE_Image\" src=\"http://tiebapic.baidu.com/forum/w%3D580/sign=c3b13838c016fdfad86cc6e6848f8cea/b569da2a2834349b6765ad9694ea15ce36d3be03.jpg?tbpicau=2023-05-01-05_b1ca63c2a2a4a2fe31b067999b9e7c40\" size=\"612764\" changedsize=\"true\" width=\"560\" height=\"995\" size=\"612764\">","author":"Xjgxjm1984000","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.f276693b.XEeKSIB8_8UeeDT5GmzAxA?t=1625918276&fr=pb","date":"2021-09-20 16:31","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":9,"title":"回复：【葛琪琪】人物分析贴","content":"理科偏才毛小蒙吐槽：<img class=\"BDE_Image\" src=\"http://tiebapic.baidu.com/forum/w%3D580/sign=2f01c28b03df8db1bc2e7c6c3923dddb/56181e385343fbf2c1706530ed7eca8065388f0e.jpg?tbpicau=2023-05-01-05_32f4218285efbe447bbb5ad1284ee4f8\" size=\"607607\" changedsize=\"true\" width=\"560\" height=\"995\" size=\"607607\">","author":"Xjgxjm1984000","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.f276693b.XEeKSIB8_8UeeDT5GmzAxA?t=1625918276&fr=pb","date":"2021-09-20 16:32","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":10,"title":"回复：【葛琪琪】人物分析贴","content":"笨蛋毛小蒙，不是网络游戏啦，是各种言情小说电影电视剧看多了(-_-)","author":"Xjgxjm1984000","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.f276693b.XEeKSIB8_8UeeDT5GmzAxA?t=1625918276&fr=pb","date":"2021-09-20 16:33","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":11,"title":"回复：【葛琪琪】人物分析贴","content":"当梦想照进现实，一场人为的针对她的“英雄救美”局开场。琪琪正处于危急时刻，一个额头帮着黑色发带打扮帅气的滑板少女从天而降，救了她（站在琪琪的视角）<img class=\"BDE_Image\" src=\"http://tiebapic.baidu.com/forum/w%3D580/sign=7606cf31ee1bb0518f24b320067bda77/6c479c45d688d43f58e552e1201ed21b0ef43b1e.jpg?tbpicau=2023-05-01-05_81fde5be396b71451854965e53c10f91\" size=\"541949\" changedsize=\"true\" width=\"560\" height=\"995\" size=\"541949\"><img class=\"BDE_Image\" src=\"http://tiebapic.baidu.com/forum/w%3D580/sign=a79efed90c3d26972ed3085565fab24f/3b200d4f78f0f736a8b18f125755b319ebc4131e.jpg?tbpicau=2023-05-01-05_c5f08b0dc8725f593a75df9075e84da4\" size=\"569623\" changedsize=\"true\" width=\"560\" height=\"995\" size=\"569623\">","author":"Xjgxjm1984000","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.f276693b.XEeKSIB8_8UeeDT5GmzAxA?t=1625918276&fr=pb","date":"2021-09-20 16:39","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":12,"title":"回复：【葛琪琪】人物分析贴","content":"琪琪心动不已，向陌生的帅气少年道谢。少年彬彬有礼地说出了那句装逼名句：“这不算什么啦，保护女生是我应该做的！”<br>少女从此沦陷。","author":"Xjgxjm1984000","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.f276693b.XEeKSIB8_8UeeDT5GmzAxA?t=1625918276&fr=pb","date":"2021-09-20 16:45","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":13,"title":"回复：【葛琪琪】人物分析贴","content":"陷入暗恋的琪琪开始偷偷观察和自己同班的上官帅。<br>心思细腻敏感的琪琪发现光鲜亮丽的帅似乎并不快乐。<img class=\"BDE_Image\" src=\"http://tiebapic.baidu.com/forum/w%3D580/sign=92444b40463b5bb5bed720f606d2d523/974c26381f30e92402e9d6da09086e061c95f755.jpg?tbpicau=2023-05-01-05_0049107a8729e6126c44f2062a3f636e\" size=\"672929\" changedsize=\"true\" width=\"560\" height=\"995\" size=\"672929\"><img class=\"BDE_Image\" src=\"http://tiebapic.baidu.com/forum/w%3D580/sign=e8ddb43433094b36db921be593cd7c00/d35263224f4a20a49f53762cd5529822730ed055.jpg?tbpicau=2023-05-01-05_1a3bdad420b2cd10bcfe049ab736718b\" size=\"610007\" changedsize=\"true\" width=\"560\" height=\"995\" size=\"610007\">","author":"Xjgxjm1984000","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.f276693b.XEeKSIB8_8UeeDT5GmzAxA?t=1625918276&fr=pb","date":"2021-09-20 16:49","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":14,"title":"回复：【葛琪琪】人物分析贴","content":"《飘》里斯佳丽有一段独白：我缝制了一套华美的衣裳，并爱上了它。这时候，艾希礼骑着马跑过来了，我便把那套衣服给他穿上，也不管合不合身。我不想看清楚他到底什么样，我一直爱着那套美丽的衣服，而不是那个人。<br>我爱的是某个我自己虚构的东西，而那个东西就像媚兰一样死掉了。<br><br>琪琪也一样，给自己造了一个“王子救公主”梦，然后上官帅踩着滑板从天而降，琪琪 就把这个梦套在小帅身上，也不管他合不合身。<br>然后琪琪就喜欢上了这个她塑造的上官帅。","author":"Xjgxjm1984000","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.f276693b.XEeKSIB8_8UeeDT5GmzAxA?t=1625918276&fr=pb","date":"2021-09-20 17:00","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":15,"title":"回复：【葛琪琪】人物分析贴","content":"对待爱情，琪琪是主动出击的。看见小帅不吃间食，便花了一个晚上时间做蛋挞，还欲盖弥彰地担心单面送他会让同学误会，便偷偷放到上官帅抽屉里，准备给他一个惊喜。（误会啥的，为什么你只给帅一个人做蛋挞，不给其他人做。你的小心思我们还会看不出来吗？瞧，脸都红了。）<br>放完蛋挞还不好意思地出去躲一会，脑海里上演甜蜜小剧场。<br>少女情怀总是诗。<br>（悄咪咪说一句，我还真不希望小帅吃到琪琪的蛋挞。习惯了女生主动示好的小帅不会喜欢琪琪，亦不会珍惜琪琪亲手做的蛋挞。说不定还会带回家让佣人扔了(-_-)）<img class=\"BDE_Image\" src=\"http://tiebapic.baidu.com/forum/w%3D580/sign=588d14bb493387449cc52f74610ed937/165c387adab44aed80daf40ff61c8701a08bfb0e.jpg?tbpicau=2023-05-01-05_32eec9e7446913f34e2a2bab76592d6d\" size=\"553878\" changedsize=\"true\" width=\"560\" height=\"995\" size=\"553878\"><img class=\"BDE_Image\" src=\"http://tiebapic.baidu.com/forum/w%3D580/sign=e61cb63150ce36d3a20483380af23a24/7960b699a9014c08d3af624e4f7b02087af4f40e.jpg?tbpicau=2023-05-01-05_3f126c84ce727c1d2a7027f7a160140d\" size=\"532285\" changedsize=\"true\" width=\"560\" height=\"995\" size=\"532285\"><img class=\"BDE_Image\" src=\"http://tiebapic.baidu.com/forum/w%3D580/sign=85c4ccd06787e9504217f3642039531b/8dd1047b02087bf4391594faafd3572c10dfcfe9.jpg?tbpicau=2023-05-01-05_fe47f1cb6554096ce1a77324ed4698d3\" size=\"509540\" changedsize=\"true\" width=\"560\" height=\"995\" size=\"509540\">","author":"Xjgxjm1984000","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.f276693b.XEeKSIB8_8UeeDT5GmzAxA?t=1625918276&fr=pb","date":"2021-09-20 17:13","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":17,"title":"回复：【葛琪琪】人物分析贴","content":"爱就大胆往前冲！<br>这个时候的琪琪还很自信，脑内小剧场竟然没有想过小帅拒绝吃蛋挞的可能。。毕竟心里认为自己是完美女生，自己亲手做的蛋挞小帅有什么理由不吃呢？<br>结果因为换座位，蛋挞被毛小蒙吃了，惹来一段孽缘😂😂。<br>后来误以为GiGi变的毛小蒙要表白。","author":"Xjgxjm1984000","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.f276693b.XEeKSIB8_8UeeDT5GmzAxA?t=1625918276&fr=pb","date":"2021-09-20 22:19","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":18,"title":"回复：【葛琪琪】人物分析贴","content":"琪琪还害羞地不知道说啥好。“毛”就补充“做的蛋挞”，被琪琪一✋拍飞。<br>哈哈哈哈😂😂，活该！<img class=\"BDE_Image\" src=\"http://tiebapic.baidu.com/forum/w%3D580/sign=ab389ccccf82b9013dadc33b438fa97e/5d557c8b4710b912ac38411586fdfc0393452220.jpg?tbpicau=2023-05-01-05_0fdae264345b851130f55c1f5ce8b0db\" size=\"512977\" changedsize=\"true\" width=\"560\" height=\"995\" size=\"512977\"><img class=\"BDE_Image\" src=\"http://tiebapic.baidu.com/forum/w%3D580/sign=bfd5972540950a7b75354ecc3ad0625c/768975899e510fb3fcf9bb848433c895d0430c82.jpg?tbpicau=2023-05-01-05_a518943c52b4e690c67852e608fa7dbb\" size=\"577586\" changedsize=\"true\" width=\"560\" height=\"995\" size=\"577586\">","author":"Xjgxjm1984000","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.f276693b.XEeKSIB8_8UeeDT5GmzAxA?t=1625918276&fr=pb","date":"2021-09-20 22:33","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":19,"title":"回复：【葛琪琪】人物分析贴","content":"直到琪琪看到Gi帅逛街。小话痨Gi Gi解释说上官帅打赌输了请吃大餐，还热情地邀请琪琪一起吃。<br>琪琪拒绝了，却又忍不住回头看她俩远去的背影。<br><br><img class=\"BDE_Image\" src=\"http://tiebapic.baidu.com/forum/w%3D580/sign=73cf412d26ec54e741ec1a1689399bfd/eb8f0446f21fbe0939930f0736600c338644ad9d.jpg?tbpicau=2023-05-01-05_5510254fd0fa0fa5b0d3ce798fcdd619\" size=\"667965\" changedsize=\"true\" width=\"560\" height=\"995\" size=\"667965\"><img class=\"BDE_Image\" src=\"http://tiebapic.baidu.com/forum/w%3D580/sign=90fb56f16d34349b74066e8df9e81521/b73b902f07082838aae66bfffd99a9014d08f133.jpg?tbpicau=2023-05-01-05_8b05e376538cdc777975a5e65cc2b640\" size=\"506405\" changedsize=\"true\" width=\"560\" height=\"995\" size=\"506405\"><img class=\"BDE_Image\" src=\"http://tiebapic.baidu.com/forum/w%3D580/sign=a9ef6ce98cc8a786be2a4a065708c9c7/a9452f3fb80e7becd817cff2722eb9389a506b9d.jpg?tbpicau=2023-05-01-05_996efa32b73aef67583951f38214b982\" size=\"625526\" changedsize=\"true\" width=\"560\" height=\"995\" size=\"625526\">","author":"Xjgxjm1984000","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.f276693b.XEeKSIB8_8UeeDT5GmzAxA?t=1625918276&fr=pb","date":"2021-09-20 22:40","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":20,"title":"回复：【葛琪琪】人物分析贴","content":"琪琪这么一个追求完美的女孩，心里一定很难过吧。也许上官帅是她顺风顺水的人生里遇到的第一个挫折。<br>也许她甚至觉得帅gi才是一对，天才少女少男，天生一对。<br>她忍不住问gigi是不是喜欢帅。憨憨gigi却说她喜欢所有人。琪琪尬笑地解释着此喜欢非彼喜欢。gigi懵了。（好奇心旺盛的她去问上官帅什么是喜欢———琪琪无意间又促进帅gi互动。）<br>这时候的琪琪开始自卑了吧。","author":"Xjgxjm1984000","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.f276693b.XEeKSIB8_8UeeDT5GmzAxA?t=1625918276&fr=pb","date":"2021-09-20 22:54","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":21,"title":"回复：【葛琪琪】人物分析贴","content":"写得乱七八糟的😂😂","author":"Xjgxjm1984000","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.f276693b.XEeKSIB8_8UeeDT5GmzAxA?t=1625918276&fr=pb","date":"2021-09-20 23:46","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":22,"title":"回复：【葛琪琪】人物分析贴","content":"大家中秋快乐哟","author":"Xjgxjm1984000","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.f276693b.XEeKSIB8_8UeeDT5GmzAxA?t=1625918276&fr=pb","date":"2021-09-21 22:14","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":23,"title":"回复：【葛琪琪】人物分析贴","content":"<img class=\"BDE_Image\" src=\"http://tiebapic.baidu.com/forum/w%3D580/sign=d27aee52db510fb37819779fe931c893/411cc2bf6c81800a2d6f29e5f43533fa838b4713.jpg?tbpicau=2023-05-01-05_6f7bf47694e55580ff8a6fe66b487faf\" size=\"538128\" changedsize=\"true\" width=\"560\" height=\"995\" size=\"538128\">","author":"Xjgxjm1984000","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.f276693b.XEeKSIB8_8UeeDT5GmzAxA?t=1625918276&fr=pb","date":"2021-09-22 18:36","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":24,"title":"回复：【葛琪琪】人物分析贴","content":"哎，前几个小时有很大的悲伤，想逃离微博，太emo了，因为我磕的一对体育圈的，全运会一个金牌一个银牌，好希望都能拿金牌的!算了，放个屁股，明天白天来看看帖子!","author":"昨天的雨xmy","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.384d87d2.u-aafvPGbvEw1Pven0fscw?t=1652882987&fr=pb","date":"2021-09-26 01:09","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":25,"title":"回复：【葛琪琪】人物分析贴","content":"琪琪真的是个好女孩!我经常觉得自己在像琪琪那样活着(当然我没有她优秀，我要是有她成绩那么好，我应该没有理由不开心)然后内心渴望着像gigi那样，少女情怀在遇见上官帅从天而降那一刻开始萌发，可是他却对琪琪的好视而不见。我觉得这感情没有对错，她喜欢他，而不知他，他喜欢她，而不得她。每一个人都在追逐着自己的喜欢，既然选择了默默地喜欢一个人那必定要承受一定的结果，希望每一个人都有自己的好结局。","author":"昨天的雨xmy","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.384d87d2.u-aafvPGbvEw1Pven0fscw?t=1652882987&fr=pb","date":"2021-09-26 17:35","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":26,"title":"回复：【葛琪琪】人物分析贴","content":"结局好坏不能轻易定义，但是希望他们自己选择的是对的","author":"昨天的雨xmy","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.384d87d2.u-aafvPGbvEw1Pven0fscw?t=1652882987&fr=pb","date":"2021-09-26 17:36","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":27,"title":"回复：【葛琪琪】人物分析贴","content":"大家国庆快乐呀<img class=\"BDE_Smiley\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\" changedsize=\"false\" src=\"https://gsp0.baidu.com/5aAHeD3nKhI2p27j8IqW0jdnxx1xbK/tb/editor/images/client/image_emoticon2.png\" ><img class=\"BDE_Smiley\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\" changedsize=\"false\" src=\"https://gsp0.baidu.com/5aAHeD3nKhI2p27j8IqW0jdnxx1xbK/tb/editor/images/client/image_emoticon2.png\" ><img class=\"BDE_Smiley\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\" changedsize=\"false\" src=\"https://gsp0.baidu.com/5aAHeD3nKhI2p27j8IqW0jdnxx1xbK/tb/editor/images/client/image_emoticon2.png\" ><br><br>琪琪国庆开心呦<img class=\"BDE_Smiley\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\" changedsize=\"false\" src=\"https://gsp0.baidu.com/5aAHeD3nKhI2p27j8IqW0jdnxx1xbK/tb/editor/images/client/image_emoticon24.png\" ><img class=\"BDE_Smiley\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\" changedsize=\"false\" src=\"https://gsp0.baidu.com/5aAHeD3nKhI2p27j8IqW0jdnxx1xbK/tb/editor/images/client/image_emoticon24.png\" ><img class=\"BDE_Smiley\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\" changedsize=\"false\" src=\"https://gsp0.baidu.com/5aAHeD3nKhI2p27j8IqW0jdnxx1xbK/tb/editor/images/client/image_emoticon36.png\" ><img class=\"BDE_Smiley\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\" changedsize=\"false\" src=\"https://gsp0.baidu.com/5aAHeD3nKhI2p27j8IqW0jdnxx1xbK/tb/editor/images/client/image_emoticon36.png\" ><img class=\"BDE_Smiley\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\" changedsize=\"false\" src=\"https://gsp0.baidu.com/5aAHeD3nKhI2p27j8IqW0jdnxx1xbK/tb/editor/images/client/image_emoticon36.png\" >","author":"Xjgxjm1984000","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.f276693b.XEeKSIB8_8UeeDT5GmzAxA?t=1625918276&fr=pb","date":"2021-10-01 22:55","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":28,"title":"回复：【葛琪琪】人物分析贴","content":"我也喜欢葛琪琪，我还站蒙琪，刘飒老贼为什么蒙琪没有he！","author":"xrzslll","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.92ab8d5a.VyU3nYEcxgO4Pcsrr-ygYA?t=1462720374&fr=pb","date":"2022-02-20 04:32","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":29,"title":"回复：【葛琪琪】人物分析贴","content":"呜呜呜我真的好希望最后葛琪琪能认清自己真正喜欢的上官帅只是自己心中虚构的完美形象而已，然后可以逐渐放下上官帅，去追寻自我，并在与毛小蒙等人的相处中逐渐摆脱对于“完美”的执念，容纳真正的不那么完美的自己，最后和毛小蒙成为朋友…至于有没有在一起，我个人还是蒙琪党希望他们在一起的","author":"123abcgdth","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.9d25de30.bldWqkQaKAUSDUVFMgVZlw?t=1486652010&fr=pb","date":"2022-04-08 22:42","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":30,"title":"回复：【葛琪琪】人物分析贴","content":"Gigi是很正常很可爱的英文名，名字寓意是博爱的。国外港台都有英文名/英文昵称叫Gigi的，比如黎姿，梁咏琪。而且念出来怎么也不会是Jiji吧。<img class=\"BDE_Smiley\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\" changedsize=\"false\" src=\"https://gsp0.baidu.com/5aAHeD3nKhI2p27j8IqW0jdnxx1xbK/tb/editor/images/client/image_emoticon1.png\" >","author":"月影微谰","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.a2bd9e40.7Pnr1XFnD8eiKVw30OAERw?t=1543159876&fr=pb","date":"2022-06-01 12:25","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":31,"title":"回复：【葛琪琪】人物分析贴","content":"其实取名随便单纯是以前就是定位低龄小孩子看的，只不过现在大伙都长大了，惨的是本来就是喜欢这种画风一直关注，现在反而要与时俱进更换画风，毕竟不能像以前一样第一部跟第二部画风差这么多吧","author":"去去去就来双鱼","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.e9409bbb.rd7N68K-jXcBwM8fEVOGiw?t=1614320923&fr=pb","date":"2022-06-10 01:00","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null}]